import React from "react";
import styles from "./Dialogs.module.css";
import {Col, Row} from "react-bootstrap";


const Dialogs = (props) => {
    return (
            <Row >
                <Col xs='7'>
                    <Row>
                        <Col xs='4'>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12'>Dialogs</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12'>Vanya</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12'>Katya</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12'>Maxim</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12'>Sveta</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12'>Natasha</Col>
                            </Row>
                        </Col>
                        <Col xs='8'></Col>
                    </Row>
                </Col>
            </Row>
    );
}
export default Dialogs;
